Class InsertionTrackingSet<T>

java.lang.Object
  java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      java.util.AbstractSet<T>
          com.davidsoergel.dsutils.collections.InsertionTrackingSet<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Iterable<T>, Collection<T>, Set<T>
public class InsertionTrackingSet<T>
extends AbstractSet<T>
implements Serializable

A Set that maintains a counter to associate the insertion order with each entry. If an entry is removed, its index stays the same. Also provides rapid reverse lookup by index.
